<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>tirumañcaṇa cālaiyil tāṉam paṇṇi Aruḷāniṉṟu
<lb n="2"/>Iruṅkoḷappāṭi viḷantaiyir kūṟṟattu tirumuṭṭat
<lb n="3"/>tu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">rāgade</hi>var rā<hi rend="grantha">jādhi</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi> vaḷanāṭṭu meṟkānāṭu 
<lb n="4"/>nāṭṭumuṭikoṇṭa coḻa<hi rend="grantha">śca</hi>tu<hi rend="grantha">rvve</hi>maṅkalattu nila
<lb n="5"/>ttil Ivvūr <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>vilaiyālum kuṭivilaiyālum
<lb n="6"/>vilaikoṇṭu Aṉupavittu Iṟaiyiṟuttu varuki
<lb n="7"/>ṟa Ivvūr kīḻpiṭākai kāvanūr Eṉṟu per kū
<lb n="8"/>ppaṭu nilattil nilam Irunūṟṟut toṇṇūṟṟiraṇ
<lb n="9"/>ṭe Eḻumākkāṇi Araikkāṇi muntirikaikkīḻ Arai
<lb n="10"/>ye Orumāvarai muntirikaikkīḻ Araiye Iraṇṭu
</p>

